original: Where are all the tablet PC users in the Alderney area?  Sometimes I feel like I'm the only one left!  I am organizing a barbecue / user group this weekend.  Lots of vegan food and fun drawing games!  Serious replies only.  Last time I posted an ad for tablet enthusiasts, I was bombarded with requests for ecstasy and guys that thought if you have a tablet PC you give hand jobs behind Pizza Stack.  Don't let digital writing die!  Visit
